Note: Only auto attacks can critically strike, but Suicune has 0% base Critical-Hit rate at all levels.

Pressure

Passive Ability

Damaging a Pokémon from the opposing team below 10% max HP and frozen by Suicune deals an additional 15% max HP as true damage to the target (sufficient damage reduction can prevent the target from being knocked out). Using a move grants a shield for 5s (up to 2 times); separately increases the crystal gauge by 1 for 5s (becoming full when increased 2 times).

Flooded areas created by Whirlpool or Surf remain for 5s; opposing Pokémon in a flooded area are marked as drenched for 3s. Freezing a flooded area with a regular move (not Unite Move) also freezes opposing Pokémon in that flooded area for 2s. Freezing an opposing Pokémon marked as drenched removes the mark; targets frozen by a regular move or by a frozen area cannot be marked as drenched for 3s afterward. Deals bonus damage when freezing opposing Pokémon with a regular move or by being in a frozen area.

50% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 200

25% SpA + 7 x (Level - 1) + 100

Attack

Auto Attack

When the crystal gauge is full, readies a boosted attack for 5s as the crystal gauge decays to 0; increasing the crystal gauge refills it to full.

Boosted attacks shoot water forward, damaging opposing Pokémon every 0.25s over 1s (up to 4 times), dealing bonus damage to frozen opposing Pokémon with each hit.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

21% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 94

10% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 44

Water Pulse

Move 1

6.00s Hindrance

Fires a pulse of water in the designated direction, damaging opposing Pokémon and shoving them for 0.5s when it hits.

Marks targets as drenched for 3s when it hits.

40% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 320

Water Pulse Upgrade Choices

Whirlpool

7.50s Area

Generates a vortex of water at the designated area, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect every 1s over 4s (up to 4 times), pulling them toward the center with each hit. If used again within 4s, moves the vortex in the designated direction, flooding the area it passes through.

Marks targets as drenched for 3s when hit.

18% SpA + 3 x (Level - 1) + 93

34% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 180

Reduces this move's cooldown by 1s.

Surf

5.00s Hindrance

Prepares an area for a big wave to pass through, then creates the wave and sends it in the designated direction after 0.75s, damaging opposing Pokémon hit by the wave and shoving them. The prepared area becomes flooded after the wave passes through it.

Marks targets hit by the wave as drenched for 3s. Hitting a pillar of ice created by Icy Wind with the wave shatters it, damaging opposing Pokémon hit.

55% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 270

Increases the damage of this move.

66% SpA + 5 x (Level - 1) + 324

Avalanche

Move 2

6.00s Hindrance

Creates snow to fall at the designated area for 1.5s, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect (up to 3 times) and decreasing their movement speed by 30% for 2s when hit. After 1.5s, drops a clump of snow at the designated area, damaging opposing Pokémon again.

The clump of snow freezes drenched targets for 2s when it hits; freezes flooded areas it drops on after 1s.

20% SpA + 2 x (Level - 1) + 160

30% SpA + 3 x (Level - 1) + 240

Avalanche Upgrade Choices

Ice Beam

7.00s Ranged

Fires an icy-cold beam of energy in the designated direction, damaging opposing Pokémon and decreasing their movement speed by 20% for 2s when it hits.

This move freezes drenched targets for 2s when it hits; freezes flooded areas it hits after 1s. A maximum of 2 uses can be kept in reserve, with a 0.5s cooldown between uses.

75% SpA + 5 x (Level - 1) + 380

Strengthens the movement speed decrease to 30%.

Icy Wind

5.00s Area

Builds up a gust of freezing air at the designated area for 0.5s, decreasing the movement speed of opposing Pokémon in the area of effect by 20% for 2s; then forms a pillar of ice, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and decreasing their movement speed by 20% for 2s once fully formed. The pillar of ice shatters after 4s, damaging opposing Pokémon again.

This move freezes drenched targets for 2s when the pillar of ice forms or when it shatters. Forming a pillar of ice on a flooded area freezes that area after 1s. A maximum of 2 uses can be kept in reserve, with a 0.5s cooldown between uses.

75% SpA + 3 x (Level - 1) + 360

75% SpA + 3 x (Level - 1) + 360

Reduces this move's cooldown by 1s.

Endless Ice Spikes

Unite Move

112s 100000 Area

Unlocks at level 9

Cleanses the user of status condition; then creates ice spikes in the designated direction, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and freezing those hit for 2s. After 2s, the ice spikes explode, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect again. This Unite Move does not directly interact with drench marks, nor does it freeze flooded areas.

Suicune can be stunned after cleansing themself and before creating the ice spikes, canceling the Unite Move and refunding 90% of the Unite Move gauge.

100% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 500

100% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 500

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% CDR, 20% Max HP Shield
